---

<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="section-title">Get in contact</h1>
    <p class="section-text">
      I'm passionate about building meaningful technology solutions and welcome opportunities to connect with like-minded professionals.
      Whether you're interested in collaborating on a project, discussing potential opportunities,
      or exploring ways we can work together - I'd be pleased to hear from you.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-methods">
      <h2 class="contact-subtitle">I'm interested in:</h2>
      <div class="interests-grid">
        <div class="interest-item">Freelance & Contract Work</div>
        <div class="interest-item">Full-time Opportunities</div>
        <div class="interest-item">Collaboration Projects</div>
        <div class="interest-item">Tech Discussions & Ideas</div>
        <div class="interest-item">General Inquiries</div>
        <div class="interest-item">Consulting</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info">
      <h2 class="contact-subtitle">How to reach me:</h2>
      <div class="contact-options">
        <div class="contact-method primary-contact">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p>Best for personal contact, discussions and project inquiries</p>
          <button>
            <a href="mailto:thevictor-con@outlook.com" class="contact-link">thevictor-con@outlook.com</a>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-method">
          <h3>LinkedIn</h3>
          <p>Perfect for professional networking and career opportunities</p>
          <button>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-husefest-6372843aa/" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Connect with me on LinkedIn
            </a>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-method">
          <h3>GitHub</h3>
          <p>Check out my code, contribute to projects, or start a discussion</p>
          <button>
            <a href="https://github.com/GGV7373" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Follow me on GitHub
            </a>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="response-info">
      <h2 class="contact-subtitle">Response times:</h2>
      <p class="response-text">
        I aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours. If you don't receive a response,
        please feel free to follow up as messages occasionally go undelivered.
        For time-sensitive matters, LinkedIn may provide the most reliable communication channel.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <p class="cta-text">
        I look forward to discussing potential opportunities and learning more about your projects.
        Please don't hesitate to reach out - I value every professional connection and inquiry.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
